images.story: A woman sits in a small boat holding a child on her lap while rowing with a paddle. A man behind her also rows the boat through the water.
Multiple motorcyclists ride along a road, some carrying passengers on the same bike. A driver drives a tuk-tuk in the traffic.
A woman, a child, and a man are each brushing their teeth with toothbrushes. They are facing the camera while brushing.
A boy hugs a girl while talking on a phone. The girl holds another phone in her hand.
Three girls sit at a table and eat cake with forks.
Three women walk outside while carrying open umbrellas for shade.
A grill is cooking pizza slices on foil while hot dogs and zucchini cook on the grates beside them.
Two women lean in with open mouths toward a large slice of pizza on a paper plate, each taking a bite from it.
A player in a blue jersey dribbles the soccer ball while a player in a white jersey runs alongside and challenges her for it.
One tennis player swings to hit a tennis ball over the net. Another tennis player stands ready near the net to return the ball.
A man turns a crank on a machine while a woman holds the lid on a blender filled with liquid.
A baseball batter is swinging a bat at home plate while the catcher behind him receives the pitch.
Two women are standing in a living room and each is swinging a game controller while playing.
A player in white runs while carrying a frisbee. A player in red closely guards him from behind on the field.
Two bears are eating pieces of a pumpkin on the ground. One bear has its face in the hollow pumpkin while the other eats a chunk nearby.
Two surfers ride along the same breaking wave as water sprays behind them.
Two men and a woman are taking bites of donuts. They are close together outdoors, holding the donuts up to their mouths.
Two motorcyclists are airborne on dirt bikes inside a building, performing jumps above a ramp.
A red truck sprays water onto a dirt track through nozzles at the back. A man is climbing on the back of the truck while it operates.
A skateboarder is airborne, jumping over a ledge while kicking his skateboard during the trick.
A baby and a toddler are lying on a bed, each drinking from a bottle.
A man in a yellow shirt reaches out to catch a flying frisbee while a man in a red shirt moves in front of him to block his attempt.
Two skateboarders ride longboards side by side on a paved road, crouching low as they move forward.
A woman and a man are cutting a decorated cake together while the man holds a bottle in his other hand.
A man sits on a bench eating a sandwich while talking on a cellphone.
A black dog jumps up to catch a flying disc in a grassy field. A tan dog stands nearby watching the black dog.
A painted scene on a vase shows two fighters thrusting spears at each other. Other figures and a chariot are depicted nearby.
A man has his hand on a baby elephant standing beside him. The baby elephant reaches its trunk toward an adult elephant nearby.
A man and a woman on the beach carry surfboards near the shoreline while other people swim in the water.
A person is typing on a keyboard. A cat is resting its head on the person’s arm near the keyboard.
A man lies on a bed while brushing his teeth. He is using a phone in his other hand.
A woman carries a baby on her back. The baby holds up a pink umbrella above them.
Two men sit on a couch, each holding a wine glass near his face and smelling the wine.
A woman points at the seated man's tie while he smiles. A man in a suit leans in and gestures toward the seated man during their conversation.
A child drinks from a bottle while standing next to a red car. The child rests a hand on the car door.
A girl sits holding and using a laptop while a man sits beside her reading a book.
A surfer walks along the beach carrying a surfboard. A dog sniffs the sand nearby.
A man walks along the sidewalk pulling a rolling suitcase. Behind him, a woman walks while pulling a small shopping cart.
Two workers are positioning a large round sign on a building facade, with one of them steadying it while the other attaches it to the bracket.
A woman pets a large dog in the foreground while another woman in a chair holds a child upside down on her lap.
A person bends down and grooms a horse's lower leg with a tool. The horse eats hay from a hanging net.
Two men are playing a video game while holding motion controllers and moving their arms.
A chef opens the wood-fired oven and holds the oven door while looking into the flames.
A man stands in the street holding up a stop sign. Nearby, a motorcyclist rides past on a motorcycle.
A woman sits on a couch talking on a phone. Next to her, a man handles a camera strap attached to a camera around his neck.
One woman holds up her phone to show the screen to the woman beside her. The other woman looks down at a phone in her hands.
A double-decker bus drives along a city street past buildings. A man walks on the sidewalk near storefronts.
A cat leans toward and sniffs a baby sitting beside it. A woman holds the cat close while watching them.
A man and a woman stand in a hallway while each uses a phone. Other people are visible farther down the corridor.
In a circus ring, a woman sits on an elephant as it balances with its front feet on a set of stools.
A rider sits on a horse at the shoreline while swinging a lasso in the air.
A woman holds a baby on her lap while using a laptop at a table.
A child reaches up to pick an apple from a tree while holding a bag for collecting fruit.
A man plays a piano while a woman stands behind him with her hands on his shoulders.
A woman stands on a man's feet while he lies on a bed using a laptop.
A boy sits on the floor playing with a wired game controller while a baby sits beside him holding a remote control.
Two uniformed women push large bags along a conveyor belt, while two other uniformed staff stand nearby.
Two giraffes stand beside a tree and eat leaves from its branches.
A police officer stands on the grass talking on a phone while a crowd of protesters in the background holds signs.
A boy and a girl each have a cracker in their mouth and are eating it while facing the camera.
A polar bear presses against the glass while a person on the other side takes a photo of it.
Several sheep are eating from a feed trough in a fenced field. A dog lies on the grass watching two lambs standing nearby.
A woman sits at a table talking on a phone while dipping a chip into salsa on her plate.
A person holds out a red frisbee toward a dog. The dog reaches its mouth toward the frisbee.
Two men in a small boat are rowing on the river. Several buffalo stand partially submerged near the shore.
Two motorcyclists are riding their motorcycles on a road while a car drives ahead in the same direction.
One player is sliding headfirst toward the base. A fielder stands by the base and catches the incoming ball.
One man in a yellow shirt throws a frisbee across the field while another man jumps with his arms up to catch it.
One player jumps and catches a flying disc overhead while another player reaches up to block him.
A surfer rides inside a breaking wave while nearby two people ride a jet ski on the water.
A pitcher has thrown a baseball toward home plate where a batter is ready to hit. The ball is in midair approaching the batter.
A man throws a frisbee across a grassy area. A dog runs after the frisbee.
Several people ride in a long boat on a river while holding umbrellas. A man at the front paddles the boat through the water.
A skateboarder rides a skateboard as it grinds along the edge of a concrete skate bowl.
A motorcyclist rides a motorcycle along the road while a yellow bus drives on the same roadway.
A soccer player in a striped jersey dribbles the ball across the field while a player in a yellow jersey runs after him.
Two soccer players leap as one heads the ball while another jumps over an opponent. Other players watch nearby on the court.
A skateboarder is riding a skateboard while grinding along the edge of a concrete structure.
A skateboarder is airborne with a skateboard while performing a trick above a ramp. The board and rider are moving together along the ramp structure.
A soccer player in a white-and-red uniform dribbles the ball across the field. Several players in dark uniforms chase after him while another white-and-red player runs nearby.
Two riders are riding their horses along the sandy beach near the ocean.
Several people are riding on elephants in a grassy area. One elephant is wading into shallow water while another stands nearby with riders on its back.
Two surfers walk toward the ocean while each carries a surfboard.
An adult elephant is eating a pile of hay. A baby elephant stands close and touches the adult with its trunk.
Two children sit on a toilet and each brushes their teeth with a toothbrush.
Two children are brushing their teeth with toothbrushes, and one of them holds a cup while brushing.
A cyclist rides a bicycle through an intersection while a police officer rides a motorcycle nearby.
Two women stand in a bedroom holding game controllers and playing a video game together.
A man walks across a cobblestone area carrying a suitcase and a large instrument case on his back. Other people are on the steps in the background.
Two boys sit by a bed holding game controllers and playing a video game.
Two people walk along a covered walkway while each carries a large red suitcase.
Two riders are riding horses along the sandy shore beside the water.
A woman and a man are brushing their teeth in front of a bathroom mirror. The man also holds a camera while brushing.
A boy holds an open striped umbrella while a girl leans in close and touches him.
A man drinks from a wine glass while a woman also drinks from her own wine glass nearby.
A woman sits on the grass and pets a black-and-white dog beside her while her other hand rests on a brown dog lying next to her.
One elephant reaches its trunk toward the tail/back area of another elephant walking ahead. A handler walks beside the elephants holding a stick and leading one elephant forward.
Several surfers walk along the shoreline while carrying their surfboards. Waves roll in behind them as they head down the beach.
Two men are riding elephants while the animals stand in shallow water. One elephant is eating plants with its trunk.
A woman sits on a couch using a laptop on her lap. A baby beside her touches and uses another open laptop.
Two surfers walk on the sand carrying surfboards toward the ocean.
A man in the foreground points at a keyboard on the desk. In the background, another man talks on a phone.
A woman and a man sit on a couch holding game controllers and playing a video game.
One woman shows a phone while the other woman looks down at the phone as they stand together holding containers.
A woman talks on a phone while using a laptop computer on a table.
A man writes notes in a notebook while a woman speaks to him across a table with a laptop.
A red double-decker bus and a modern coach are traveling along a city street in two separate views.
Two riders are riding horses through shallow water at the beach during sunset.
Two people are working on laptops, with hands typing on the keyboards and one hand using the touchpad.
A woman on the right hands a blender pitcher to a woman on the left, who holds it with both hands.
